<h4 id="overview">Overview</h4>
<p>
    <strong>CustomTemplateDirective</strong> is a base class for template directives that control template instantiation and projection.
</p>

<h4 id="status">Status</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4">
    <strong>Concept Phase:</strong> The API and implementation are still being designed. This plug is planned but not yet implemented.
</p>

<h4 id="intended-use">Intended Use Cases</h4>
<ul class="list-disc ml-5 mb-4 text-sm text-gray-600">
    <li>Structural directives that conditionally render template content</li>
    <li>Template repetition (loops/iterations)</li>
    <li>Content projection and slot management</li>
    <li>Lazy template instantiation</li>
</ul>

<p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-4">
    See <a href="/projects/webdirectives/">Web Directives</a> for the broader directive system.
</p>
